snippet.title: Tanzanite Crush
snippet.description:
Tanzanite Crush is very addictive and exciting adventure match 3 game filled with colorful gem crunching effects! Swap and match jewels your way, show your best strategical moves to get highest scores and pass hundred of levels. Be the jewel star and unlock all castles in Tanzanite Crush Jewel games.
